Attribution and Citation Notice

This repository is licensed under Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International
(CC BY 4.0): https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

Minimum legal requirement for reuse of repository content:
- give appropriate credit,
- provide a link to the CC BY 4.0 license,
- indicate whether changes were made.

Preferred scholarly credit practice (strong request):
- cite this repository in publications, reports, and benchmark writeups that
  use or adapt its methods, protocol, terminology, or conclusions,
- include an acknowledgment that this work introduced the specific reused
  material.

Preferred citation metadata:
- CITATION.cff
- CITATION.bib

Detailed policy and recommended attribution language:
- docs/reference/attribution_and_citation_policy.md
